children.value: This module provides Cython-level wrappers for all primary routines included in LAPACK 3.4.0 except for
since its interface is not consistent from LAPACK 3.4.0 to 3.6.0. It also provides some of the fixed-api auxiliary routines.
These wrappers do not check for alignment of arrays. Alignment should be checked before these wrappers are used.
To remove in the future –– scipy.linalg.cython_lapack
